descriptionHtml:
Athena female nord level 1, she is at Riverwood just ready to begin her adventures.

This save file don\'t need any mods to work, however to make she look like the screenshots you will need the following:

- AOF Believable Hair -Female and Male- by AnOldFriend
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4307

- Coverwomen by mrLenski (look 1)
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3563

- Natural Eyes 1_3 by nevenbridge
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3589

I also highly suggest:
- Realistic Colors and Real Nights v14 with HDR by aLaaa
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1875

You may use other facial textures you like, she will just look different, worse or even better.
You may also use \"showracemenu\" in the console to adjust her hair-eye style/color to your liking
but keep in mind she will lose all her makeup in the process.
author: tupaz
